ts suggest that tokens should be prevented from trading on intermediary markets that do not comply with royalty schemes, but this standard only provides a functionality for non-intermediary NFT trading and does not offer a ... ## [] Backwards Compatibility\nThis standard is compatible with[ERC-721] and[ERC-2981].\n## [] Reference Implementation ```\n`// SPD"
